{
  "texts": [
    "Implementation Impact.",
    "We evaluate the performance of original implementations of the best performing methods on 1B experiments, i.e., Vamana, HNSW, and ELPIS against optimized methods from the ParlayANN library [98] (Vamana_Opt, HNSW_Opt, and HCNNG_Opt) on Deep1B.",
    "(a) Deep (b) SALD (c) Seismic (d) Sift (e) RandPow0 (f) RandPow50 Fig. 13.",
    "25GB datasets (a) Deep (b) Sift Fig. 14.",
    "100GB datasets (a) 1% noise (b) 10% noise Fig. 15."
  ]
}